OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start, with isolated
OL,6,Fmist and fog patches soon clearing.
OL,7,FThe clouds will bubble up to give a
OL,8,Fmixture of sunny spells and showers,
OL,9,Flocally heavy, with risk of hail and
OL,10,Fthunder, during the afternoon. Light
OL,11,Fwinds. Feeling warmer.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FEarly evening showers fading
OL,14,Fto leave a dry night, with prolonged
OL,15,Fclear spells. Turning chilly, with a
OL,16,Ftouch of frost in prone rural spots.
OL,17,FSome isolated mist and fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
